profile:
Alliance Elevator is a full service elevator contractor serving all of Ontario. 
Our service virtues are the backbone of our organization. We take tremendous pride in upholding the principles our company was founded upon by bringing a level of personalized care and attention that has since escaped our competition. With a seasoned team of expert elevator technicians and an extensive inventory of parts, we are fully prepared to provide repairs, maintenance, assessment and testing services for nearly every elevator brand in operation. We have the fastest response and repair completion times because no other company in Ontario has the same level of dedication to their customers.
